e">https://www.amazon.com/dp/158642436X?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>导师的残骸</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/1324096322?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9781324096320.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;《导师的残骸》埃里克·杰·多林 (Eric Jay Dolin)&lt;br /&gt;该故事讲述了 1832 年捕鲸船失事中幸存的 11 名船员与帕劳原住民的故事。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1324096322?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>这片土地和它的人民</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/0316264830?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9780316264839.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;《土地及其人民》作者：大卫·塞达里斯 (David Sedaris)&lt;br /&gt;关于时间的流逝、复杂的关系和生活中一些意想不到的乐趣的文章。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 04:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/0316264830?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>邻家英雄</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/1668093804?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9781668093801.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;邻家英雄玛莎·拉达兹 (Martha Raddatz)&lt;br /&gt;这位荣获艾美奖的 ABC 新闻主播介绍了 9/11 事件后服役的美军成员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 04:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1668093804?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>我们所说的一切</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/0593595122?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9780593595121.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;我们所说的一切作者：Ben Rhodes&lt;br /&gt;这位奥巴马总统的前演讲撰稿人通过这本 15 篇演讲集阐释了作为美国人的意义。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 04:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/0593595122?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>公共利益的危机</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/037462111X?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/97803746